<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Sweet Joy — Pastelería Artesanal · Trujillo</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --rose: #f4a7b9;
    --rose-dark: #c97a93;
    --rose-light: #fde8ef;
    --gold: #c9a84c;
    --gold-light: #fdf3dc;
    --cream: #faf6f0;
    --beige: #f0e9dc;
    --text: #3a2a2e;
    --text-mid: #7a5c65;
    --white: #fff;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; background: var(--cream); color: var(--text); }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(250,246,240,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ecddd5;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 5%;
    height: 68px;
  }
  .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; text-decoration: none; }
  .nav-logo-icon { font-size: 28px; }
  .nav-logo-text { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; }
  .nav-logo-sub { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-mid); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; display: block; line-height: 1; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { color: var(--text-mid); text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; transition: color .2s; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--rose-dark); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--rose); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 9px 20px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none; transition: background .2s;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--rose-dark); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nav-links { display: none; }
  }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh; padding: 68px 0 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rose-light) 0%, var(--cream) 50%, var(--gold-light) 100%);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 60%, rgba(244,167,185,0.2) 0%, transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 30%, rgba(201,168,76,0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; padding: 60px 5%; }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block; background: var(--rose-light); color: var(--rose-dark);
    border: 1px solid var(--rose); border-radius: 20px; padding: 5px 16px;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(44px, 8vw, 88px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--rose-dark); }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 18px); color: var(--text-mid);
    max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 36px; line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300;
  }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-main {
    background: var(--rose); color: white; border-radius: 32px;
    padding: 14px 32px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none; transition: all .2s; border: none; cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(244,167,185,0.4);
  }
  .btn-main:hover { background: var(--rose-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(244,167,185,0.5); }
  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent; color: var(--text); border: 2px solid var(--beige);
    border-radius: 32px; padding: 13px 28px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none; transition: all .2s;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--rose); color: var(--rose-dark); }
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex; gap: 48px; justify-content: center; margin-top: 60px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .hero-stat { text-align: center; }
  .hero-stat-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--rose-dark); }
  .hero-stat-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-mid); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-top: 2px; }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .section-divider { height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--rose), transparent); margin: 0 10%; }

  /* SECTION HEADER */
  .sec-head { text-align: center; padding: 80px 5% 40px; }
  .sec-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rose-dark); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .sec-head h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 48px); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.15; }
  .sec-head h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--rose-dark); }
  .sec-head p { color: var(--text-mid); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 14px; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* FILTER TABS */
  .filter-tabs { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 0 5% 36px; }
  .ftab {
    padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 24px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer; border: 1.5px solid var(--beige); background: var(--white);
    color: var(--text-mid); transition: all .2s;
  }
  .ftab.active, .ftab:hover { background: var(--rose); border-color: var(--rose); color: white; }

  /* PRODUCT GRID */
  .products-section { background: var(--cream); padding-bottom: 80px; }
  .pgrid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(270px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px; padding: 0 5%;
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .pcard {
    background: var(--white); border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid #ecddd5;
    transition: transform .25s, box-shadow .25s;
  }
  .pcard:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(201,122,147,0.15); }
  .pcard-img-wrap { position: relative; height: 220px; overflow: hidden; }
  .pcard-img-wrap img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transition: transform .4s; }
  .pcard:hover .pcard-img-wrap img { transform: scale(1.06); }
  .pcat-badge {
    position: absolute; top: 12px; left: 12px;
    color: white; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 12px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }
  .pcard-body { padding: 18px; }
  .pcard-body h3 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 17px; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pcard-body p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .pcard-footer { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
  .pprice { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; color: var(--rose-dark); font-weight: 700; }
  .btn-pedir {
    background: var(--rose); color: white; border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 7px 16px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none; transition: background .2s;
  }
  .btn-pedir:hover { background: var(--rose-dark); }
  .pcard.hidden { display: none; }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rose-light) 0%, var(--gold-light) 100%);
    padding: 80px 5%;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center;
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; }
  }
  .about-text .eyebrow { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rose-dark); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .about-text h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 40px); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .about-text h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--rose-dark); }
  .about-text p { color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .about-pills { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 24px; }
  .pill {
    background: white; border: 1px solid var(--rose); color: var(--rose-dark);
    border-radius: 20px; padding: 6px 14px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;
  }
  .about-img-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
  .about-img-grid img { width: 100%; height: 180px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 16px; }
  .about-img-grid img:first-child { grid-column: 1/-1; height: 220px; }

  /* HOW TO ORDER */
  .how-section { padding: 80px 5%; background: var(--cream); }
  .steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 32px; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding-top: 10px; }
  .step { text-align: center; }
  .step-num {
    width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--rose-light); border: 2px solid var(--rose);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; color: var(--rose-dark); font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
  }
  .step h3 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 17px; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .step p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* TESTIMONIALS */
  .reviews-section { background: var(--beige); padding: 80px 5%; }
  .reviews-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .review-card { background: var(--white); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #ecddd5; }
  .review-stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .review-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .review-author { font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text); }
  .review-role { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-mid); }

  /* CTA BANNER */
  .cta-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rose-dark) 0%, #8b3a52 100%);
    padding: 80px 5%; text-align: center; color: white;
  }
  .cta-banner h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .cta-banner p { font-size: 16px; opacity: .85; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 32px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .btn-white {
    background: white; color: var(--rose-dark); border-radius: 32px;
    padding: 14px 32px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; transition: all .2s;
  }
  .btn-white:hover { background: var(--cream); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  /* CONTACT */
  .contact-section {
    padding: 80px 5%;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .contact-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; } }
  .contact-info h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 32px; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .contact-item { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .contact-icon { font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .contact-item strong { display: block; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); }
  .contact-item span { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-mid); }
  .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea, .contact-form select {
    width: 100%; padding: 12px 16px; border: 1.5px solid #ecddd5;
    border-radius: 10px; font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit;
    background: var(--cream); color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 12px;
    outline: none; transition: border .2s;
  }
  .contact-form input:focus, .contact-form textarea:focus { border-color: var(--rose); }
  .contact-form textarea { min-height: 100px; resize: vertical; }
  .contact-form .btn-main { width: 100%; text-align: center; border: none; font-family: inherit; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--text); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    padding: 40px 5%; text-align: center; font-size: 13px;
  }
  footer .footer-logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; color: white; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  footer a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration: none; }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--rose); }
  footer .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; margin: 16px 0; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* WA FLOAT */
  .wa-float {
    position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 24px; z-index: 200;
    width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #25d366; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(37,211,102,0.4);
    text-decoration: none; font-size: 28px; transition: transform .2s;
  }
  .wa-float:hover { transform: scale(1.12); }

  /* CART ICON IN NAV */
  .nav-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
  .cart-icon-btn {
    position: relative; background: var(--rose-light); border: 1px solid var(--rose);
    width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer; font-size: 17px; transition: background .2s;
  }
  .cart-icon-btn:hover { background: var(--rose); }
  .cart-count-badge {
    position: absolute; top: -6px; right: -6px;
    background: var(--rose-dark); color: white; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
    min-width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 9px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 0 4px; line-height: 1; border: 2px solid var(--cream);
  }
  .cart-count-badge.hidden-badge { display: none; }

  /* CART OVERLAY + DRAWER */
  .cart-overlay {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(58,42,46,0.45);
    z-index: 300; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity .25s;
  }
  .cart-overlay.open { opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }
  .cart-drawer {
    position: fixed; top: 0; right: 0; height: 100vh; width: 400px; max-width: 92vw;
    background: var(--cream); z-index: 301; box-shadow: -8px 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    transform: translateX(100%); transition: transform .3s ease;
  }
  .cart-drawer.open { transform: translateX(0); }
  .cart-drawer-head {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 20px 22px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ecddd5; background: var(--white);
  }
  .cart-drawer-head h3 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; color: var(--text); }
  .cart-close-btn {
    background: none; border: none; font-size: 22px; color: var(--text-mid); cursor: pointer;
    width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; transition: background .2s;
  }
  .cart-close-btn:hover { background: var(--beige); }
  .cart-items-list { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 14px 18px; }
  .cart-empty { text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; color: var(--text-mid); }
  .cart-empty span { font-size: 40px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .cart-item {
    display: flex; gap: 12px; padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ecddd5;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .cart-item img { width: 64px; height: 64px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .cart-item-info { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .cart-item-info h4 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .cart-item-info .ci-price { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-mid); }
  .cart-item-controls { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-top: 8px; }
  .qty-btn {
    width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1.5px solid var(--beige);
    background: var(--white); color: var(--text); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all .2s;
  }
  .qty-btn:hover { border-color: var(--rose); color: var(--rose-dark); }
  .qty-val { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; min-width: 18px; text-align: center; }
  .cart-item-right { text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .cart-item-subtotal { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-weight: 700; color: var(--rose-dark); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .cart-remove-btn {
    background: none; border: none; color: var(--text-mid); font-size: 12px; cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: underline; padding: 0;
  }
  .cart-remove-btn:hover { color: var(--rose-dark); }
  .cart-drawer-footer { padding: 18px 22px; border-top: 1px solid #ecddd5; background: var(--white); }
  .cart-total-row {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .cart-total-row span:first-child { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-mid); }
  .cart-total-row .cart-total-amount { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 24px; color: var(--rose-dark); font-weight: 700; }
  .cart-checkout-form input {
    width: 100%; padding: 10px 14px; border: 1.5px solid #ecddd5; border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; background: var(--cream); color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 10px; outline: none; transition: border .2s;
  }
  .cart-checkout-form input:focus { border-color: var(--rose); }
  .btn-checkout {
    width: 100%; background: #25d366; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 13px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer;
    transition: background .2s; font-family: inherit;
  }
  .btn-checkout:hover { background: #1ebd59; }
  .btn-checkout:disabled { background: #cfd8d3; cursor: not-allowed; }
  .toast-msg {
    position: fixed; bottom: 90px; right: 24px; z-index: 400;
    background: var(--text); color: white; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 14px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); transition: all .25s; pointer-events: none;
  }
  .toast-msg.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cart-drawer { width: 100vw; }
    .toast-msg { right: 14px; left: 14px; bottom: 90px; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo" id="erpSecretLogo" onclick="handleLogoClick(event)">
    <span class="nav-logo-icon">🍓</span>
    <div>
      <span class="nav-logo-text">Sweet Joy</span>
      <span class="nav-logo-sub">Pastelería Artesanal</span>
    </div>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#productos">Carta</a></li>
    <li><a href="#nosotros">Nosotros</a></li>
    <li><a href="#como-pedir">Cómo pedir</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contacto">Contacto</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="nav-actions">
    <button type="button" class="cart-icon-btn" onclick="openCart()" title="Ver carrito" aria-label="Ver carrito">
      🛒<span class="cart-count-badge hidden-badge" id="cartCountBadge">0</span>
    </button>
    <a href="https://wa.me/51907034487" target="_blank" class="nav-cta">💬 Pedir ahora</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="hero-badge">🍰 Pastelería Artesanal · Trujillo</span>
    <h1>Dulces que<br><em>enamoran</em> el paladar</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Tortas personalizadas, brownies, alfajores, frappés y jugos naturales. Hechos con amor y los mejores ingredientes para cada ocasión especial.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#productos" class="btn-main">🎂 Ver carta completa</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/51907034487" target="_blank" class="btn-outline">💬 Pedir por WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-num">500+</div><div class="hero-stat-label">Clientes felices</div></div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-num">14</div><div class="hero-stat-label">Productos artesanales</div></div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-num">S/ 12</div><div class="hero-stat-label">Desde</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- PRODUCTS -->
<section class="products-section" id="productos">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">🍩 Nuestra carta</div>
    <h2>Preparado con <em>amor y frescura</em></h2>
    <p>Cada producto es elaborado con ingredientes frescos y seleccionados. Sin conservantes, con mucho cariño.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="filter-tabs">
    <button class="ftab active" onclick="filterProducts('Todos', this)">Todos</button>
    <button class="ftab" onclick="filterProducts('Tortas', this)">🎂 Tortas</button>
    <button class="ftab" onclick="filterProducts('Bebidas', this)">🥤 Bebidas</button>
    <button class="ftab" onclick="filterProducts('Bocaditos', this)">🍪 Bocaditos</button>
  </div>
  <div class="pgrid">
    
